{"tid":445522,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"開個投票台算啦","createTime":"2017-10-23T12:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T03:23:41.000Z","uid":63845,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a4998551fe2f6415385697d2667a98ab23c7388","tid":445522,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:49:55.000Z","msg":"俾班小學雞投飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a9809da67fbe66fffae2aead10de18c8a6dbbb","tid":445522,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:54:32.000Z","msg":"正常開post講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8affbffdc2c75cf5395555697a84553cf0d803e0","tid":445522,"uid":20736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"開就正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔開就負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f909f2a8b65a3a63f0981a9ae6b43ddf9fc69dd2","tid":445522,"uid":147949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"未又係上哂熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47796c9378ccf533fcce02011e7febebf5caad2c","tid":445522,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:58:52.000Z","msg":"真心炆<br />\n以往見到正評多既post=好笑/高質<br />\n今日見到個3000正評個post<br />\n原來係問女友係咪有左bb<br />\n<br />\n除左開既人有問題 投既人都on9"},{"pid":"e7412347c9283ee6cbf9444cf99a48f9c7e9dae7","tid":445522,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a182b5607a1595ac90e1296d2a3b33122a2d54d4","tid":445522,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:10:47.000Z","msg":"一個二個開埋晒啲<br />\n認同A觀點就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認同B觀點就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你問我，呢班人係咪真心熱愛投選運動而做呢種事，以我觀察黎睇，好明顯唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就等我抽樣搵少少例子<br />\n<br />\n[二選一] 靜靜雞 定 靜雞雞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/445235\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/445235</a><br />\n呢類就最為垃圾既，乜柒都無直接彈兩行野叫人投，不過呢個post就天有眼，無人理佢，抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n揸車嘅你地 會唔會讓斑馬線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/439945\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/439945</a><br />\n同上，都係果啲引人望完個正負就會輕易有答案既垃圾post，而呢個更加有幾百人投添，無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[有圖]係火車無啦啦有條女係我張床<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/445123\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/445123</a><br />\n呢個相對黎講已經算好啲，本來一路都有圖有字，但好可惜條友最後都係屎忽痕要整返個投票調查，而好明顯個風向都實係吹向佢set做正評果個option架啦，結果又成為一個make到noise上熱門既廢post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過有好就當然會有更加廢既，而最令人覺得肉酸既係呢類post誇起上黎往往係可以比人煲到上千even數千正評，咁我一開頭就話係心理唔平衡既人為呃正評先會開呢類post<br />\n<br />\n不過由我一路打呢篇野一路搵資料啦<br />\n我發現如果話晒佢地係心理唔平衡而咁做，的確係太過主觀有欠公允，所以我又得出左另一個原因<br />\n就係呢類人表達能力極度有問題，佢地唔開呢類正負評post就無辦法進行正常既討論，如果你講野mean啲，直頭可以稱呢類人係智障都完全無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當然無論以上人士係心理唔平衡又好定表達能力有缺撼都好，我都會建議佢地立即就醫，唔好再沉溺連登損人不利己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實搞公投，舉行投選活動就無罪既，但如果係濫用左就當然唔可取，呢啲人開埋晒呢啲問東問西或者係邊條女正啲既post，好啦問完之後又有咩用呢，任何投選投票都一定有佢自身既出發點，如果投完之後根本無下文無用處既，唔單止浪費資源，仲對真心熱愛投票活動既朋友仔都好唔公平，因為真係令投票既本質改變晒，搞到低質晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁成日開無聊投票既低質會員睇到呢度，以後仲會唔會咁做？希望你呢啲垃圾識諗喇快啲收手喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823e045af3c1ee9a96d085d1f913c4a1ea8fa9c1","tid":445522,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T19:12:36.000Z","msg":"食M記鍾意食硬薯條定軟薯條？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/445861\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/445861</a><br />\n<br />\n又一個，你食野咪食，問黎做咩，投票既意義同真諦係咁樣用？唔問過之後唔通會食唔到？"},{"pid":"433f749def0c7fe4d66496abad0d01c09c523c2f","tid":445522,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 投票台<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公投台"},{"pid":"c6fa754e61603b7db832dfab5478a8ee18554427","tid":445522,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T00:34:38.000Z","msg":"當呢到Facebook咩"},{"pid":"4b3848d99eaaa8a3acf667331ef12a2ad2ff688b","tid":445522,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個二個開埋晒啲<br />\n認同A觀點就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認同B觀點就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你問我，呢班人係咪真心熱愛投選運動而做呢種事，以我觀察黎睇，好明顯唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就等我抽樣搵少少例子<br />\n<br />\n[二選一] 靜靜雞 定 靜雞雞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/445235\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/445235</a><br />\n呢類就最為垃圾既，乜柒都無直接彈兩行野叫人投，不過呢個post就天有眼，無人理佢，抵死<img src=\"/assets/